WEBVTT

00:00.795 --> 00:02.176
<i>Previously on Fringe...</i>

00:02.443 --> 00:04.962
You are looking through
a window into another world.

00:05.248 --> 00:07.705
An alternate universe,
just like ours

00:07.853 --> 00:10.634
and in each of them,
there is a version of us.

00:10.869 --> 00:12.706
I can't let Peter die again.

00:12.757 --> 00:14.508
Walter, Peter is dead.

00:14.575 --> 00:15.742
I'm talking
about the other Peter.

00:15.793 --> 00:18.095
The one on the other side.

00:20.798 --> 00:22.933
Thrust into another universe,

00:23.017 --> 00:25.185
and took a son
that wasn't mine.

00:25.252 --> 00:27.604
I'm going to be
waiting for you right here

00:27.672 --> 00:30.924
- bring him back to me.
- I promise.

00:30.975 --> 00:34.044
Hold on tight, son.

00:34.112 --> 00:36.763
You're not my father, are you?

00:36.814 --> 00:39.583
Of course I am.

